2、创建一个叫riding的计分板
/scoreboard objectives add riding dummy
给僵尸马上有僵尸的马设置分数为1
/scoreboard players set @e[type=EntityHorse] riding 1 {Type:3,Passengers:[0:{id:"Zombie"}]}
给所有僵尸马设置分数为0，用比上面慢一点的高频
/scoreboard players set @e[type=EntityHorse] riding 0
然后修改NBT
entitydata @e[type=EntityHorse,score_riding_min=1] {Invulnerable:1}
entitydata @e[type=EntityHorse,score_riding=0] {Invulnerable:0}
